title: What About Origins? -  Dr A J Monty White   epub/mobi
description:
Dr Monty White examines the presuppositions and assumptions which underlie the evolutionary philosophy and he carefully examines the 'scientific method' of evolutionists. The author is a respected scientist himself and well qualified to speak about the scientific method. His conclusion is that it is simpler and more rational to believe in a creator than in the theory of evolution, although that, of course, involves a willingness to believe in processes other than the gradual ones proposed and believed to have happened by those who have faith in the evolutionary hypothesis.
